Section: text
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/thuruht/q3n
Description: Quote Triple-Slash Notation — manage quoted text collections
 Q3N is a plain-text file format and toolchain for storing
 quotations, citations, and annotated excerpts with source URIs.
 .
 This package provides:
  • q3n CLI   — create, search, edit, export Q3N files
  • Python library  — core/q3n.py for integration
  • Q3N Manager GUI — graphical browser/editor (python3 gui/app.py)
 .
 Entries use the simple /// … \\\ delimiter notation with
 support for https, file, ISBN, DOI, arXiv, and custom URIs.
